From 03e216e0d5f440c65a272db14bdebb910f37a3e1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Thu, 8 Jan 2026 01:27:41 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 8/8] arm: gxp: add miscellaneous platform support

Add miscellaneous drivers and platform support for HPE ProLiant systems:

AMD APML (Application Platform Management Link):
- AMD processor monitoring via sideband interface
- SBRMI (Sideband Remote Management Interface) driver
- APML SB-TSI temperature sensor interface

Ampere SMpro:
- smpro-errmon: Error monitoring for Ampere processors
- smpro-misc: Miscellaneous Ampere processor utilities

UBM (Universal Back Module):
- ubm4: Storage backplane management driver

Additional updates:
- LED GPIO driver enhancements for device removal support
- Build system updates (drivers Kconfig/Makefile, scripts/Makefile.lib)

Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>

